graph LR
    ODHModelCtrl[ODH Model Controller<br/>v1.27.0]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    ODHModelCtrl -->|core platform| KServe[KServe v0.12.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|ingress| OSRoutes[OpenShift Routes API v3.9+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies - Conditional
    ODHModelCtrl -->|serverless mode| Knative[Knative Serving v0.39.3<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|mesh integration| Istio[Istio Service Mesh v1.19.4<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|mesh integration| Maistra[Maistra ServiceMesh v2.x<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|authentication| Authorino[Authorino v0.15.0<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|monitoring| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.64.1<br/>CONDITIONAL]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    ODHModelCtrl -.->|metadata tracking| ModelReg[Model Registry v0.1.1<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHModelCtrl -->|reads config| ODHOp[ODH Operator<br/>DSC/DSCI CRDs]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|consumes secrets| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Data Connections]
    ODHModelCtrl -.->|coordinates| ModelMeshCtrl[ModelMesh Controller<br/>Multi-model serving]

    %% Platform Services
    ODHModelCtrl -->|TLS certs| ServiceCA[OpenShift service-ca-operator]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|reconciliation| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

    %% Integration Points - Downstream
    Dashboard -->|creates ISVCs via| ODHModelCtrl
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy| ODHModelCtrl

    %% External Services
    ODHModelCtrl -->|model storage| S3[S3 Storage]
    ODHModelCtrl -->|runtime images| Registry[Container Registry]

